        "q1": "<div style='background-color: #f1f2f6; border-left: 5px solid #6c5ce7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;'><strong style='display: block; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 5px;'>Part 1: Questions 1-10</strong><span style='font-size: 0.9rem; color: #57606f;'>Questions 1-4: Choose the correct letter, <strong>A</strong>, <strong>B</strong> or <strong>C</strong>.</span></div><div style='display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px;'><div style='background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;'><p style='margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: bold;'><span class='question-badge'>1</span> 1. Why does she call this doctor?</p><input type='hidden' id='ans-1' value=''><div class='option-group' data-question='1'><div class='option-item' data-value='A'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>A</strong> He is popular among oversea students.</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='B'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>B</strong> The advertisement says he is excellent.</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='C'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>C</strong> She heard that he was a good doctor.</span></div></div></div><div style='background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;'><p style='margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: bold;'><span class='question-badge'>2</span> 2. How does the sickness affect the woman?</p><input type='hidden' id='ans-2' value=''><div class='option-group' data-question='2'><div class='option-item' data-value='A'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>A</strong> It interrupts work.</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='B'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>B</strong> It keeps her awake at night.</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='C'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>C</strong> It makes her feel anxious.</span></div></div></div><div style='background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;'><p style='margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: bold;'><span class='question-badge'>3</span> 3. What does the doctor want to know?</p><input type='hidden' id='ans-3' value=''><div class='option-group' data-question='3'><div class='option-item' data-value='A'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>A</strong> how long she has suffered from the problem</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='B'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>B</strong> whether she has suffered headaches before</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='C'><span class='option-text'><strong>C</strong> what caused the headache</span></div></div></div><div style='background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px;'><p style='margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: bold;'><span class='question-badge'>4</span> 4. What does the doctor suggest doing first?</p><input type='hidden' id='ans-4' value=''><div class='option-group' data-question='4'><div class='option-item' data-value='A'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>A</strong> taking some medicine</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='B'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>B</strong> having an optic examination</span></div><div class='option-item' data-value='C'><span class='option-radio'></span><span class='option-text'><strong>C</strong> wearing glasses when using a computer</span></div></div></div></div><div style='background-color: #f1f2f6; border-left: 5px solid #6c5ce7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;'><strong style='display: block; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 5px;'>Questions 5-6</strong><span style='font-size: 0.9rem; color: #57606f;'>Complete the sentences below. Write <strong>NO MORE THAN THREE WORDS</strong> for each answer.</span></div><div style='background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.8;'><p style='margin-top: 0; font-weight: bold;'>In order to get to the optic examination centre, she should:</p><ul style='list-style-type: none; padding-left: 5px;'><li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>• Take a turn at the <span class='question-badge'>5</span> <input type='text' id='ans-5' style='width: 180px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ced6e0; border-radius: 6px; outline: none;'></li><li style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>• Then turn left at the <span class='question-badge'>6</span> <input type='text' id='ans-6' style='width: 180px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ced6e0; border-radius: 6px; outline: none;'> crossroad.</li></ul></div><div style='background-color: #f1f2f6; border-left: 5px solid #6c5ce7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;'><strong style='display: block; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 5px;'>Questions 7-10</strong><span style='font-size: 0.9rem; color: #57606f;'>Complete the table/notes below. Write <strong>NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS AND/OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</span></div><div style='background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e4e7eb; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; line-height: 1.8;'><h3 style='margin-top: 0; color: #6c5ce7; border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f2f6; padding-bottom: 8px;'>Personal information</h3><ul style='list-style-type: none; padding-left: 5px;'><li style='margin-bottom: 10px;'>• Name: Anu Bhatt</li><li style='margin-bottom: 10px;'>• Address: <span class='question-badge'>7</span> <input type='text' id='ans-7' style='width: 180px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #ced6e0; border-radius: 6px; outline: none;'> Road</li><li style='margin-bottom: 10px;'>• Postcode: <span class='question-badge'>8</span> <input type=